      "content": "yeah i get that. but i'm wondering if there's more to it. like, if you compare the actual clarity of the messages, they both basically say the same thing. is it just the grammar, or is there a specific vibe or \"personality\" you're picking up on in the second one that makes it feel \"less professional\"?",
