      "content": "that's fair. i guess i'm just wondering if the \"vibe\" changes depending on who is sending it. like if an employee from a different cultural background or someone who uses certain dialects uses that style, does it make them actually look less competent or less serious to a manager? or is it just about the words themselves?",
